English: <color=red>://ERROR: Door in emergency lockdown, unable to operate.</color> Establish a connection to <color=orange>[SANTONIAN_WIRE_UGC343]</color> to proceed.
Description: A text string that appears on screen when the player attempts to open a door which is locked due to an emergency lockdown. Don't alter the RichText tags.

French.Translation: <color=red>://ERREUR : verrouillage d'urgence de la porte enclenché, opération impossible. </color> Établissez une connexion avec <color=orange>[SANTONIAN_WIRE_UGC343]</color> pour continuer.

German.Translation: <color=red>://FEHLER: Tür in Notverriegelung, Bedienung nicht möglich.</color> Stellen Sie eine Verbindung zu <color=orange>[SANTONIAN_WIRE_UGC343]</color> her, um fortzufahren.

Spanish.Translation: <color=red>://ERROR: Puerta en cierre de emergencia. No se puede operar.</color> Establece conexión con <color=orange>[SANTONIAN_WIRE_UGC343]</color> para continuar.

Korean.Translation: <color=red>://오류: 문이 비상 폐쇄 상태여서 작동 불가능합니다.</color> <color=orange>[SANTONIAN_WIRE_UGC343]</color>에 연결해 진행하십시오.
